Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十七幕\N告白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我「希望」这词语的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 不正是您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.10,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何您一言不发
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话已无法传达给您了…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是想这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「这世上没有偶然」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该早已告诉过您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一切都是必然」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛若不是知道你父亲真实身份的证人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我身边有何价值？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.70,0:04:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若不是蒙代戈之子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何我非在Luna与你相识…不可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.20,0:04:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始伯爵就…将我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我装作与你偶遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微的利用了一下你的信任与有情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那种小玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「怎么会…」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一开始伯爵就…将我…」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎 说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:04:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟从一开始就设计了这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 伯爵不是一直在帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一直都关心着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与您共同渡过的日子竟然都是骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想沉浸在那天真的幻想之中…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:06:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我明知那天海黛将在议会揭露一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还特地邀你去旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.10,0:06:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至今为止真的帮了我很大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决斗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真经典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武将之子必须固守形式…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是明晨五时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布洛涅森林
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盔甲和剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔图乔 你做我的证人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自始至终认真看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 我正式接受决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明晨五时见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是停留在今时今日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只属于我们的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都不能取消吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和阿尔贝先生的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您让我「自由地生活」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才苟延残喘至今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若…您失去生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.20,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也无法再活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩窟王啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没…时辰还未到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎兹…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都那么关心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我总是…不听你的话 自把自为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 弗郎兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦擦鼻涕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！那不是正中他下怀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种决斗 立即给我取消
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会当我的见证人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会生气也是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这是我无论如何都必须去做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好 伯爵一开始就打算杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白去当他复仇的牺牲品也无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他欺骗我 敷衍我诱我上钩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以最卑鄙的手段愚弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的生活全盘打乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不能原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若伯爵曾是你母亲的未婚夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你父亲因为太过爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二十五年前让伯爵背上莫须有的罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强夺了他的未婚妻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙·唐泰斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙代戈夫人来访
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.70,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是爱德蒙·唐泰斯本人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想见您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这二十五年来 我没有一刻忘记过您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道您无法原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次 只要一次就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.10,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我和身为爱德蒙的您对话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身体只留下他的躯壳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本人已不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.40,0:13:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话为何我从刚见到您那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就预感到您是爱德蒙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这冰冷的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此无法可想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德蒙 您曾经思念的人已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我证明给您看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明晨五时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布洛涅森林恭候驾临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经晚了 弗郎兹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.30,0:15:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论过去伯爵与父亲直接发生过什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些事已无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和伯爵之间发生的事 已无可挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那么恨我的话就赶快杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟玩弄了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝 不行 别去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来 阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今仍要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎兹 回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 刚才还在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过太好了 那天起完全联系不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.20,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真的很担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过弗郎兹回来得正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗郎兹 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是阿尔贝的生日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才来找你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 少迷糊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我为阿尔贝谱了一首曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还没完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不符合欧仁妮风格的浪漫曲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 明天在老地方咖啡馆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.70,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、你和阿尔贝开个派对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就说有朋友的发表会什么的 溜出来就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 能拜托你点事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给他写了生日卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个年纪了又不好意思亲手交给他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 年纪怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正只有我看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有点原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我走之后你再交给阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.70,0:19:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给他个惊喜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我继续作曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天 下午三点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.50,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老地方咖啡馆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你 来看望我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您平安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.90,0:20:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为红方的胜利干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为白方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是黑方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.30,0:20:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要打垮他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 根本不足为俱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划破拂晓的剑刃之音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我手持愤怒之剑 斩断欺骗与虚伪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八幕\N决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
